    section.section-6.guides#guides
        p.section-phrase GUIDES
        h3.tertiary-heading Let our expert&rsquo;s guide you
        .guides-saying
            +guideTestimonial("Adam", "Welcome, fellow explorers, to a magnificent voyage through time and place. Over the course of this extraordinary tour, we will delve deep into the annals of history, unraveling the enigmatic past of this illustrious city, and at the same time, we will traverse its vibrant streets, steeped in tradition and teeming with life", "/img/guide/guide-1.avif")
